      description: ["Bound tools can be activated by shift + right click. They are already uniquely powerful, but feature a chargable right-click for massive clearing capabilities, extending in all directions and upwards!", "", "Using these tools draws upon your life network - or your lifeforce, should you run out. Use with caution!"],
