      ],
      description: ["Welcome to Blood Magic!", "", "Blood Magic is a magic mod centered around gaining power from sacrifice.", "", "It offers a lot of cool gadgets such as the &1Sigils&r, not to mention a variety of building blocks.", "", "The &6Sanguine Scientiem &rcontains information on nearly all of Blood Magic, so for the most part, I'll be referring to that."],
