          id: "0300000003C90000",
          type: "item",
          item: "bloodmagic:altar"
        }
      ],
      description: ["The Blood Altar is the main crafting mechanic of Blood Magic - It infuses Life Essence (Blood) into items to transform them.", "", "It's a multiblock structure, that gets bigger with each tier. You can use the &4Inspectoris Scandalum&r to visualize where the runes and such should be placed.", "", "See the Sanguine Scientiem for details.", "", "Since the altar grows downwards with each tier, it is recommended you plan ahead accordingly. Currently, the altar is only implemented until tier 5, with tier 6 requiring creative mode spawned items. Keep that in mind when laying the foundations!"],
      icon: "bloodmagic:altar",
      dependencies: ["0200000003C80000"],
      rewards: [
