        }
      ],
      description: ["Slates are magically charged pieces of stone. They can be crafted by placing a smooth stone block on a blood altar with blood available. A tier 1 altar can only produce blank slates, but as the altar grows, so does its ability to charge the slate further.", "", "Slates are used for many recipes, but first and foremost they enable the creation of runes that can be used to extend and empower your blood altar.", "", "See the Sanguine Scientiem for details."],
